      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Ad column April 26 about Internet television start-up Joost; Nick Loria is senior vice president</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Advertising column in Business Day yesterday, about the start-up of Joost, the Internet television service, misidentified Nick Loria, a Joost executive who explained the company's advertising formats. He is senior vice president for global advertising, not general manager of North American sales and operations.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
